        <div n="911-62GH" type="poem"><head type="note" n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-1"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-1-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-1-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="underline">By Dr </hi>Swift<hi rend="underline"> to my Lady</hi> Carteret.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="2" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-2"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-2-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-2-line-group-1-line-1"><hi rend="underline">The Answer to the Riddle in our next</hi>.</l></lg></head><head type="note" n="3" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-3"><lg n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-3-line-group-1" type="headnote"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-headnote-3-line-group-1-line-1"/></lg></head>
      <lg n="1" type="stanza"><l n="1" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-1"><hi rend="display-initial">F</hi>ROM <hi rend="underline">India</hi>'s burning clime I'm brought,</l><l n="2" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-2"> With cooling gales like zephyrs fraught.</l><l n="3" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-3"> Not <hi rend="underline">Iris</hi> when she paints the sky,</l><l n="4" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-4"> Can shew more different hues than I;</l><l n="5" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-5"> Nor can she change her form so fast,</l><l n="6" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-6"> I'm now a sail, and now a mast.</l><l n="7" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-7"> I here am red, and there am green,</l><l n="8" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-8"> A beggar there, and here a queen.</l><l n="9" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-9"> I sometimes live in house of hair,</l><l n="10" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-10"> And oft in hand of lady fair.</l><l n="11" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-11"> I please the young, I grace the old,</l><l n="12" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-12"> And am at once both hot and cold.</l><l n="13" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-13"> Say what I am then, if you can,</l><l n="14" xml:id="spp-911-62GH-line-14"> And find the rhime, and you're the man.911-62GH   </l></lg></div>
      </div>
